lead_paragraph: Zlatan Ibrahimovic played chief tormentor when he scored two goals and set up the others in Paris St Germain's 4-1 home victory over Stade de Reims in Ligue 1 on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Ibrahimovic on Fire as PSG Beat Reims
headline.main: Ibrahimovic on Fire as PSG Beat Reims
